<h1><icon-wc name="sparkles" size="sm"></icon-wc> Effects Pack</h1>
<p class="lead">Niche text and visual effects: glitch, typewriter, scramble, blur-reveal, animate-image, ticker, and star-rating.</p>

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr><th>Type</th><td>Functional</td></tr>
    <tr><th>Version</th><td>1.0.0</td></tr>
    <tr><th>CSS</th><td><code>packs/effects.full.css</code></td></tr>
    <tr><th>JS</th><td><code>packs/effects.full.js</code></td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<section>
  <h2>What's Included</h2>

  <h3>Components</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/elements/web-components/rating/"><code>&lt;star-rating&gt;</code></a> &mdash; three-layer star rating widget with CSS-only base and JS enhancement</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Data Attribute Effects</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-text-effects/"><code>data-glitch</code></a> &mdash; RGB split glitch text effect</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-text-effects/"><code>data-typewriter</code></a> &mdash; character-by-character typing animation</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-text-effects/"><code>data-scramble</code></a> &mdash; random character scramble reveal</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-text-effects/"><code>data-blur-reveal</code></a> &mdash; blur-to-sharp text entrance</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-animate-image/"><code>data-animate-image</code></a> &mdash; play/pause control for animated GIF, WebP, APNG</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/attributes/data-ticker/"><code>data-ticker</code></a> &mdash; animated number count-up on scroll</li>
  </ul>
</section>

